BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 158.16 740 Td (MELTDOWN vs TANTRUM - WHAT'S THE DIFFERENCE?) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 705 Td (Sometimes people think a meltdown is 'bad behavior.' It is NOT.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 688 Td (A meltdown is your brain's OVERLOAD response. Here's the difference:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 671 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 654 Td (MELTDOWN:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 637 Td (  - Happens when your brain gets TOO MUCH input) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 620 Td (  - You CANNOT control it \(it's like a computer crashing\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 603 Td (  - You feel WORSE during and after) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 586 Td (  - It can happen even when you're alone) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 569 Td (  - You need LESS input and a safe space to recover) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 552 Td (  - It is NOT your fault) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 535 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 518 Td (TANTRUM:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 501 Td (  - Happens to get something you want) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 484 Td (  - Stops when you get what you want) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 467 Td (  - You're somewhat in control of it) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 450 Td (  - Needs an audience) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 433 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 416 Td (IMPORTANT MESSAGE: If you have meltdowns, you are NOT bad.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 399 Td (Your brain processes the world differently. That's okay.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 382 Td (The goal is to recognize the WARNING SIGNS early so you can) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 365 Td (get to a safe place BEFORE full overload.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 348 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 331 Td (My early warning signs that a meltdown is coming:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 314 Td (  1. ____________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 297 Td (  2. ____________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 280 Td (  3. ____________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 263 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 246 Td (What helps me during a meltdown:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 72 229 Td (  ________________________________________________________) Tj ET

