BT 0 g /F5 18 Tf 232.56 740 Td (A MESSAGE FOR YOU) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 700 Td (Dear Reader,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 680 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 660 Td (Having big emotions is not a bad thing.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 640 Td (It means you feel things deeply. That is a STRENGTH.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 620 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 600 Td (Your brain works differently from some other kids.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 580 Td (That does not mean it works WRONG.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 560 Td (It means the world wasn't designed for your brain,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 540 Td (so you have to work a little harder sometimes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 520 Td (That's not fair. But you are stronger than you know.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 500 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 480 Td (Some days will be hard. Some days you will feel) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 460 Td (overwhelmed or frustrated or sad.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 440 Td (That's okay. Those feelings will pass.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 420 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 400 Td (You are not 'too much.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 380 Td (You are not 'broken.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 360 Td (You are not 'bad.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 340 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 320 Td (You are a person who is LEARNING.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 300 Td (And every single day you practice,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 280 Td (it gets a tiny bit easier.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 260 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 240 Td (Be patient with yourself.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 220 Td (You are doing great.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 200 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 12 Tf 100 180 Td (- This workbook believes in you.) Tj ET

